queen Sunmi on new song Noir|website=philstar.com|access-date=2019-03-15}}</ref> It is her first single in 2019 and  it follows her last year's album, titled [[Warning (Sunmi EP)|Warning]].\n\n==Composition==\n\"Noir\" was written by Sunmi and produced by EL CAPITXN. \n\nThe title of the song literally translates to ''black'' in [[French]], but can also refer to [[Noir fiction]], a subgenre of [[crime fiction]] characterized by its bleak and [[Nihilism|nihilistic]] tone. \n\nIt was described as a \"electronic retro dance fusion with dreamy synths, disco drums, and trendy 808 bass\".<ref>{{cite news|title=Noir by Sunmi on Genius|url=https://genius.com/Sunmi-noir-lyrics|website=Genius|accessdate=August 11, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Critical reception==\n\nTamar Herman from [[Billboard (magazine)|''Billboard'']] described the song as a \"captivating, lo-fi pop track, which is a hot take on the perils of trying to live it up on social media\".<ref>{{cite news|title=Sunmi Tackles Performative Nature Of Social Media in 'Noir' Video: Watch|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/8500832/sunmi-noir-video|website=Billboard|accessdate=August 11, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Promotion==\nSunmi performed Noir at the music show ''[[M Countdown]]'' on April 11, 2019 and during her first world tour, 'Warning'.{{citation needed|date=August 2019}}\n\n==Music video==\nThe music video for the single was released on March 4, 2019. As of August 2019, it has over 17 million views on [[YouTube]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CNeNwplE_aw|title=MV] SUNMI(\uc120\ubbf8) _ \ub204\uc544\ub974(Noir)|accessdate=August 7, 2019|publisher=1theK|via=[[YouTube]]}}</ref>\n\n== Track listing ==\n* ''[[Music download|Digital download]]''\n# \"Noir\" \u2013 3:29\n\n==Charts==\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br>position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| South Korea ([[Gaon Digital Chart