-chau-finishes-among-top-10-of-miss-supranational-2019-595932.html|title=Ngoc Chau finishes among Top 10 of Miss Supranational 2019|website=vietnamnet.vn|accessdate=7 December 2019}}</ref>\n|'''Miss Supranational Asia'''\n'''Winner - Supra Chat with Valeria Episode 2'''\n\n'''2nd Place Miss Elegance'''\n|[[Vietnam's Next Top Model (season 7)]] (Winner)\n\nMiss Supranational Vietnam 2018 (Winner)\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n\n\n[[Category:Beauty pageants in Vietnam]]\n", "name_user": "BD2412", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:Fixing links to disambiguation pages, improving links, other minor cleanup tasks", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miss_Supranational_Vietnam"}
